name: Michael
dialog: Welcome back, Senpai! Did you miss us?

name: Lucifer
dialog: You seem stronger than before...we should spar later!

name: Dracula
dialog: Don't you think you've been away for too long? Did you bring anything for me? I want fresh "blood"!

name: Saint
dialog: Don't forget to fill me in on everything that you've learned about the truth of this world on your journey!

name: KongMing
dialog: I want to know what happened in your journey too!

name: KongMing
dialog: Iron Fist? She was delighted after hearing about your return.

name: KongMing
dialog: Sadly she is otherwise engaged and couldn't make it today. However, she did ask me to pass a letter to you. Here it is!
